\SE\SE[0]Welcome back, Laura. \SE[0]How was your work? Were
you okay?

\SE[3]Yeah. Ryan and the others did their best too. \SE[1]I
fell into the river, so I might catch a cold...

\SE\SE[0]Yeah. It seems like you're feeling good today.
\SE[0]Is it because it was sunny at noon?

\SE[3]I have a souvenir for you. \SE[1]I bought some cream
puffs, so come down and eat them. \SE[5]If you don't hurry,
Vita might eat them all.

\SE[55]You should rest a little. \SE[56]Luna, I'll keep an
eye on you, so...
\SE[2]Hmm... Well then... \SE[0]I'll let you do that.

\SE\SE[0]Ah, that's right. \SE[1]I already washed your body
today, so you're fine. \SE[0]After one more hour, I'll help
you move your body.

\SE[3]I'm back, Luna. \SE[1]Today, you know... I conquered a
fortress? \SE[2]Ryan and the others helped me...

\SE[5]Those kids... \SE[7]Vega trained them and they became
really strong, so if you see them, you might be surprised...

\SE[4]Ah, that's right. \SE[44]I also studied a little bit
of magic. \SE[4]I don't have much aptitude for it, but...

\SE[55]To be able to fight alone and healing magic....
\SE[44]Learning them was really tough.... I had Vega as my
teacher....

\SE[43]I studied a lot while getting scolded...
\SE[56]Rebecca and Lunaroa who can actually use their skills
properly are amazing... I couldn't help but be impressed.

\SE[44]I've worked hard to become able to use it.... \.I
want you to see it later.... \!\SE[21]I want you to say Wow,
amazing!....\.I want you to praise me....

\SE[59]Huh...\.Your hair is in three braids at the ends...?
\SE[57]Ah...\.It's Vita, right? She sometimes unexpectedly
acts like a girl...\.That girl...

\SE[45]Hehe... I think it's a bit childish for Luna, but...
\SE[56]But, it's cute. It suits her.

\SE[23]Because it's a life that was saved by Luna...
\!\SE[18]This time, it's my turn... to save Luna...

\SE[39]Even if Luna says Don't help me!!, I will definitely
help her. \SE[55]That's how absolute it is.

\SE[39]So... just a little longer.... \SE[55]Please wait for
me....

\SE[56]I tried to act tough... but... \SE[43]The truth is...
I'm lonely...

\SE[59]Can I get a little closer to you? \!\SE[57]Ah, even
if you say no, I'll still go. \!\SE[43]... If I start
crying, I'm sorry.
